
Graph - Network of Nodes.
Node - Nodes are known as vertex(vertices).
Edge - Connection between the nodes.
* Type of Edge:-
1.Uni-Directional/Directed ( X------>Y )
2.Bidirectional/Undirected ( X-------Y )

Weight - Weight is the number or value associated with edge.It can represent time, distance, cost, etc.
it can have any value +ve,-ve and 0 too.

Size of Graph = Total no. of vertices.
Neighbour - Adjacent nodes are Neighbours of each other.

How to Store graph in memory
(Representation of Graph in the Memory)


